<D>__{ferris?}
<C>__{joyce}
<D>__{he doesn't have a fever. but he says his stomach hurts and he's seeing spots.}
<A>__{close up. ferris his lifeless eyes blink.}
<L>__{interior bedroom. parents}
<A>__{tom bends down and touches ferris' forehead.}
<C>__{tom}
<D>__{what's the matter, ferris?}
