<D>__{maybe i should call the office and tell them i won't be in.}
<C>__{ferris}
<D>__{i'm okay, mom. i feel perfectly...oh, god!}
<A>__{he's gripped by a seizure. his body stiffens and he chokes. his older sister, jeanie, walks into the room. she's dressed for school. she's cute and stuck up. a major pill.}
<C>__{jean}
<D>__{oh, fine. what's this? what's his problem?}
