<D>__{please don't be upset with me, jeanie. be thankful that you're fit and have your health. cherish it.}
<C>__{jeanie}
<P>__{(to herself)}
<D>__{oh, i wanna puke.}
<A>__{she glares at ferris. her eyes are mascara and vengence. she slips out of the room. ferris' brother, todd and sister, kimberly peek into the room.}
